data.description: Welcome home in Spring Valley Lake! This lovely house offers resort-style living and an array of amenities!!. You will get to enjoy a 200-acre lake perfect for water sports, a beautiful beach area for sunbathing & swimming plus 14 fishing areas for the avid angler. The community center provides a hub for social gatherings and activities, while the 24-hour security patrol ensures peace of mind. If you're looking to elevate your lifestyle, joining the Bear Valley Country Club inside Spring Valley Lake is an enticing option. Here, you can indulge in the challenging 18-hole Robert Trent Jones championship golf course, play tennis, pickle ball or racquetball, work out in the fitness center, take a refreshing swim in the Olympic sized swimming pool or relax in the jacuzzi or sauna. This charming home features a front porch and deck welcoming guests with a grand double-door entry. The layout is perfect for entertaining, with a formal living and dining area plus breakfast bar. The kitchen is sure to impress with its modern design, granite countertops, pantry and plenty of cabinets.  A breakfast bar seamlessly connects the kitchen to the family room with vaulted ceilings, complete with a fireplace that creates a warm and inviting atmosphere for you to gather. The master bedroom with vaulted ceilings, features a walk-in closet.  Convenience is key with an indoor laundry room and cabinets for additional storage. Two-car attached garage  plus side door for convenience to get to the fully fenced backyard. 2 sheds that stay too! Enclosed patio could be used a bonus room/craft room/office. Overall, this home provides functionality, making it a place where you can truly feel at ease and proud to call home.
